details.alternate_methods:
You can also apply by post.

You’ll need to fill in a [claim form](http://hmctsformfinder.justice.gov.uk/HMCTS/GetForm.do?court_forms_id=608 "claim form"){:rel="external"} and return it to your [local county court.](http://hmctscourtfinder.justice.gov.uk/HMCTS/ "local county court"){:rel="external"}

##Scotland

If you live in Scotland, you can use your local [sheriff court.](http://www.scotcourts.gov.uk/locations/index.asp "sheriff court"){:rel="external"}
